{"thag3.13:0.1":"Theragatha 3.13 ","thag3.13:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.13:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.13:0.4":"Abhibhutattheragatha ","thag3.13:1.1":"“Sunatha natayo sabbe, ","thag3.13:1.2":"yavantettha samagata; ","thag3.13:1.3":"Dhammam vo desayissami, ","thag3.13:1.4":"dukkha jati punappunam. ","thag3.13:2.1":"Arambhatha nikkamatha, ","thag3.13:2.2":"Yunjatha buddhasasane; ","thag3.13:2.3":"Dhunatha maccuno senam, ","thag3.13:2.4":"Nalagaramva kunjaro. ","thag3.13:3.1":"Yo imasmim dhammavinaye, ","thag3.13:3.2":"appamatto vihassati; ","thag3.13:3.3":"Pahaya jatisamsaram, ","thag3.13:3.4":"dukkhassantam karissati”ti. ","thag3.13:3.5":"… Abhibhuto thero …. "}